description: This file defines a React functional component named HomeScreen125171, which renders a static, pixel-perfect layout of a home screen for a notes application. It includes various styled divs, images (mostly icons and background elements), and text elements that mirror a Figma design. The component also utilizes useEffect for initial logging purposes.
